OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fwill quickly clear then a dry day with
OL,7,Fplenty of warm sunshine. Becoming very
OL,8,Fwarm again in the west.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening.
OL,11,FRemaining dry overnight with clear
OL,12,Fspells but some low cloud will develop
OL,13,Fin the east. A warm night in the west.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FLow cloud in the east will
OL,16,Fsoon burn back to the coast, Otherwise
OL,17,Fit will be another dry and sunny day.
OL,18,FVery warm in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
